         <abstract>
            <p>This paper, in the first place, calls attention to an extraordinarily compact solution of the problem in the title, given (a trifle hidden) in the work of the late Jacques Touchard. Its main weight, however, is on properties of the several kinds of number sequences appearing.</p>
